  allLines:
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 940a91f339e1825439b9f6d15b9c98fa, type: 3}
    sentence: "So, confession time. I actually hadn\u2019t read the last volume of
      The Neptunian Beast but I got my hands on it after our date and it was amazing.
      Love it when... I really can\u2019t talk about that anymore huh...\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: -1160322238068995058, guid: e79cf994b0112f542bb5904bcd06966b, type: 3}
    sentence: 'Oh I know right! I reread the part where the shapeshifter goes absolutely
      nuts on the apple of destruction, like ten times.



'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Oh she destroyed the apple alright.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Hah, yeah... And the part where she used her tentacles to-

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Psst. Hey, Chap! Shoot- Stop\u2019em, quickly! They\u2019re getting
      too freaky. Unless you wanna go to celestial prison for privacy invasion!\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Huh- Oh god okay--

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Guysss! Forgive me for butting in, I\u2019m aware you are having a
      blast talking about the book but unfortunately, we are not allowed to record
      explicit conversations during assisted dates.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'I fully encourage you to continue once my job here is done, though!

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "You know, you\u2019re a real pain in the ass.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Elroi! She\u2019s just doing her job. Although it is Venus, like,
      there are literal booths for you-know-what in this bar...\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Oh yeah, miss killjoy over here would veto that right away as well,
      wouldn\u2019t you now?\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Oh, come on. We are having fun chatting here, aren\u2019t we? We don\u2019t
      have to talk about comics. Tell me, have you had any fun shoots recently?\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: No.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Oh. Uh okay then! '
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'So, in that case, what do you wanna talk about? '
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 
    eventTrigger: 
